_sText:
This is my 2nd skill-surf map with 5 stages.
There are two jails, one is only available if someone finished the map. Then he can use an unique slay method (at least i hope that its unique ^^).

The other jail, where people get into when they fail the map, has been made by Ryan S. Thank you very much for that ;)

Furthermore, I want to thank Surf-Velocity because Wirelezz hosted the beta-tests on their server.


Here's Miggo's vid of the map (watch in HD!):
